  "sectionId": "s6",
  "content": "<details>\n  <summary><strong>️ 종교활동</strong></summary>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"note\">⚡ 제공된 강의 자막에는 종교활동에 대한 내용이 포함되어 있지 않습니다. 따라서 해당 섹션의 내용은 비어 있습니다.</div>\n  </div>\n</details>\n<details>\n  <summary><strong>시험 핵심 키워드</strong></summary>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>분류</th>\n          <th>키워드</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주요 종교</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">대종교</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">불교</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">천도교</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">동학</span>), <span class=\"keyword\">천주교</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">원불교</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주요 인물</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">박중빈</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">한용운</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주요 단체/활동</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">중광단</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">의민단</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">북로군정서</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">새생활 운동</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">3·1운동</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주요 출판물/잡지</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">만세보</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">개벽</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">신여성</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">어린이</span></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</details>",
